data.description: Get ready to fall in love with this 2 bedroom, 2 bath home located in SE Minot! This home has been meticulously maintained and exquisitely remodeled.  Upon entering the home you will be welcomed by an adorable and very convenient mud room area that leads into an open concept living and dining room.  While here, take notice of the new white trim and doors and the LVP flooring throughout! On this level you will also find one bedroom large enough to accommodate a king size bed and perfectly located right next to the main floor, completely updated, full bathroom.  The bright and spacious kitchen has lots of counter and storage space for all of your culinary needs and has newer stainless steel appliances as well.  There is plenty of room for a second table for your morning coffee!  In the basement you will find a mostly finished laundry room/maintenance room that even has a folding counter for all the future loads of laundry that you will be doing in your washer and dryer that comes with the property.  On this level is a second living space, large full bath and second bedroom that features a shiplap wall!  As we continue our tour, we can exit the kitchen back door onto a large deck that overlooks a large, fenced back yard!  And let's not forget the detached single car garage that is insulated and fully finished.  The updates to this home include LVP flooring, white trim and doors, newer windows, newer shingles, newer appliances, cement board siding, insulated garage, large fenced yard, newer AC unit, large deck and is beautifully updated. Don't let this property pass you by and call for a showing today!
